## What I Worked On Today

NIST SP 800-50 provides the framework for building a security awareness and training program. The AT-2 control family (Literacy Training and Awareness) in NIST SP 800-53 Rev 5 defines the requirements. Today I build the complete second-year training program design: role-differentiated curriculum, delivery mechanisms, the phishing simulation program design, measurement framework, and the honest gap assessment that connects training effectiveness to the risk register.

